com.bigdata.relation.rule

Interface IStarJoin<E>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BOp, Cloneable, IPredicate<E>, IPropertySet, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SPOStarJoin
    Deprecated. 
    This is not currently supported. It was implemented, but we did not find improved performance for it.

    public interface IStarJoin<E>
extends IPredicate<E>
    Interface for a special type of IPredicate - the star join predicate. This type of predicate bypasses the normal join operation and does a binding set join of the matches to its star constraints from within the access path operation.
    Author:
    Mike Personick
